'''霍華德·泰勒·立克次'''（{{lang-en|Howard Taylor Ricketts}}，{{bd|1871年|2月9日|1910年|5月3日|catIdx=Ricketts, Howard Taylor}}），生於[[美國|美國]][[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[芬德利|芬德利]]（Findlay）<ref name = RoID>{{Citation| last = Weiss| first = Emilio | last2 = Strauss | first2 = Bernard S. | coauthors = | title = The Life and Career of Howard Taylor Ricketts | work = | publisher =  The University of Chicago | journal = Reviews of Infectious Diseases | volume = 13 | issue = | pages = 1241–2 | date = 27 December 1990 | origyear = 1991 | url = http://cid.oxfordjournals.org/content/13/6/1241.full.pdf | format = PDF | doi = | accessdate = 28 April 2011}}</ref>，著名[[病理學|病理學家]]，為[[立克次體|立克次體]]的發現者。

==生平==
他最早在[[西北大学_(伊利诺州)|西北大學]]研究[[芽生菌病|芽生菌病]]。之後到[[芝加哥大學|芝加哥大學]]，在[[蒙大拿州|蒙大拿州]]研究[[落磯山斑點熱|落磯山斑點熱]]，研究過程中，發現這個疾病的致病源是一種[[立克次體|立克次體]]，後來它被命名為[[立氏立克次體|立氏立克次體]]<ref>{{Cite journal | last = Margulis | first = Lynn | authorlink =  | coauthors = Betsy Palmer Eldridge | title = What a Revelation Any Science Is! | journal = ASM News | volume = 71 | issue = 2 | pages = 65–70 | publisher = The American Society for Microbiology | location =  | year = 2005 | language =  | url = http://www.asm.org/asm/files/ccLibraryFiles/Filename/000000001350/znw00205000065.pdf | format = PDF | jstor =  | issn =  | doi =  | id =  | mr =  | zbl =  | jfm =  | accessdate = 28 April 2011 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110722231400/http://www.asm.org/asm/files/ccLibraryFiles/Filename/000000001350/znw00205000065.pdf | archivedate = 2011年7月22日 | df =  }}</ref><ref name="PrescotMicro">{{cite book|last1=Willey|first1=Joanne|last2=Sherwood|first2=Linda|last3=Woolverton|first3=Chris|title=Prescott's microbiology.|year=2010|publisher=McGraw-Hill Higher Education|location=New York|isbn=978-0077350130|edition=8th ed.}}</ref> 。

1910年，在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]進行研究時，因感染[[斑疹傷寒|斑疹傷寒]]而去世<ref>{{Cite web | last = Enersen | first = Ole Daniel | authorlink =  | coauthors =  | title = Who Named It? A dictionary of medical eponyms | work =  | publisher =  | date = 1994–2011 | url = http://www.whonamedit.com/doctor.cfm/3334.html | format = website | doi =  | accessdate = 28 April 2011 | archive-date = 2017-09-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170920045154/http://www.whonamedit.com/doctor.cfm/3334.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

